property.value:
■ This creature costs 1 less to summon for each of your opponent's creatures. It can't cost 0 or less.
{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ When you put this creature, destroy all creatures that have 5000 power or less.

{QUATTRO BREAKER}
■ Whenever your opponent would put a creature with an ability that starts with "When you put this creature", your opponent puts that creature into its owner's mana zone instead.
■ During your turn, you may summon a creature from your mana zone.
